UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 555
1 A RESOLUTION confirming the appointment of Heather Graham to the Kentucky
2 Agricultural Development Board.
3 WHEREAS, on July 6, 2025, in accordance with KRS 248.707 and by virtue of
4 Executive Order 2025-008, Commissioner Jonathan Shell appointed Heather Graham to
5 the Kentucky Agricultural Development Board for a term expiring July 6, 2029; and
6 WHEREAS, the appointment is subject to Senate confirmation; and
7 WHEREAS, Heather Graham has been determined to meet the requirements of
8 KRS 248.707, representing active farmers;
9 NOW, THEREFORE,
10 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
11 Kentucky:
12 Section 1. The Senate hereby confirms the appointment of Heather Graham to
13 the Kentucky Agricultural Development Board.
14 Section 2. The Clerk of the Senate shall forward a copy of this Resolution and
15 notification of its adoption to Heather Graham of Campton, Wolfe County, Kentucky,
16 and to Commissioner Jonathan Shell, Corporate Drive Complex, Frankfort, Kentucky
17 40601.
